It's just one of my many identities.

1080
00:50:15,940 --> 00:50:18,150
I would prefer you call me

1081
00:50:19,150 --> 00:50:21,040
a theoretical experimenter.

1082
00:50:22,010 --> 00:50:23,040
What does it mean?

1083
00:50:23,490 --> 00:50:24,920
For example, stand-up comedy.

1084
00:50:25,050 --> 00:50:26,150
I discovered that stand-up comedy

1085
00:50:26,150 --> 00:50:27,960
has its own inherent patterns.

1086
00:50:28,690 --> 00:50:30,300
So I spent some time

1087
00:50:30,300 --> 00:50:32,440
creating a joke generator.

1088
00:50:33,260 --> 00:50:34,100
Yes,

1089
00:50:34,170 --> 00:50:36,040
do you know what a joke generator is?

1090
00:50:37,610 --> 00:50:39,110
No worries, let me explain slowly.

1091
00:50:39,570 --> 00:50:42,080
He talks just like my teacher lecturer.

1092
00:50:42,210 --> 00:50:44,080
The audience hates being
lectured the most.

1093
00:50:44,940 --> 00:50:48,300
He said it like a rotten cherry.

1094
00:50:48,300 --> 00:50:50,400
It has no stem.

1095
00:50:50,570 --> 00:50:52,420
You only need to remember one keyword.

1096
00:50:52,420 --> 00:50:54,310
It's called Expectation Violation.

1097
00:50:54,420 --> 00:50:55,520
Let me give you an example.

1098
00:50:56,670 --> 00:50:59,010
When I first took over our company,

1099
00:50:59,010 --> 00:51:01,480
