difficult time for the company.

1100
00:51:01,940 --> 00:51:02,940
I remember very clearly,

1101
00:51:02,940 --> 00:51:04,520
at that time, the major shareholder

1102
00:51:05,050 --> 00:51:07,490
put this mess on me

1103
00:51:07,490 --> 00:51:08,980
like sending away the God of Plague.

1104
00:51:08,980 --> 00:51:10,520
Then he disappeared without a trace.

1105
00:51:10,940 --> 00:51:13,280
So under my painstaking management,

1106
00:51:13,280 --> 00:51:15,590
the company went completely bankrupt
in less than one year.

1107
00:51:17,530 --> 00:51:19,150
You must think I would say,

1108
00:51:19,460 --> 00:51:20,910
under my painstaking management,

1109
00:51:20,910 --> 00:51:22,380
the company turned losses into profits

1110
00:51:22,380 --> 00:51:23,660
and got better and better, right?

1111
00:51:23,820 --> 00:51:24,900
But I didn't say that.

1112
00:51:24,900 --> 00:51:26,880
This is called Expectation Violation.

1113
00:51:28,590 --> 00:51:30,290
Of course, the company
did not go bankrupt.

1114
00:51:30,290 --> 00:51:32,360
Otherwise, I wouldn't be
standing here today.

1115
00:51:32,940 --> 00:51:34,380
Through my diligent management,

1116
00:51:34,380 --> 00:51:37,400
the company truly turned around
and is getting better and better.

1117
00:51:38,010 --> 00:51:40,300
So the unfortunate major shareholder

1118
00:51:40,300 --> 00:51:43,150
must now regret even
more than Ronald Wayne.

1119
00:51:51,980 --> 00:51:53,590
Do you not know

1120
00:51:53,900 --> 00:51:55,560
who Ronald Wayne is?

1121
00:51:56,380 --> 00:51:57,360
Don't you watch...?

1122
00:51:58,340 --> 00:51:59,180
Okay.

1123
00:52:00,860 --> 00:52:02,050
Ronald Wayne

1124
