1127
00:52:07,210 --> 00:52:09,560
for 800 USD.

1128
00:52:10,010 --> 00:52:12,190
Isn't that funny?

1129
00:52:12,530 --> 00:52:14,260
10%, if converted to today's value,

1130
00:52:14,260 --> 00:52:16,090
would be 60 billion USD.

1131
00:52:16,090 --> 00:52:17,630
He sold it for 800 USD.

1132
00:52:17,980 --> 00:52:18,990
If I had been there,

1133
00:52:18,990 --> 00:52:19,940
I would have given him 1,000.

1134
00:52:19,940 --> 00:52:21,420
And I wouldn't let him give me change.

1135
00:52:21,420 --> 00:52:23,530
No, I would tell him,
"Keep your change".

1136
00:52:23,530 --> 00:52:25,150
Because he doesn't understand Chinese.

1137
00:52:27,780 --> 00:52:28,620
Good!

1138
00:52:39,940 --> 00:52:41,630
