on the spot.

1150
00:53:09,690 --> 00:53:10,530
What?

1151
00:53:10,780 --> 00:53:11,620
What?

1152
00:53:16,170 --> 00:53:17,380
Let me share with you

1153
00:53:17,380 --> 00:53:19,080
