1154
00:53:19,780 --> 00:53:21,960
Okay, I'm already sweating.

1155
00:53:22,340 --> 00:53:24,010
Are you very curious

1156
00:53:24,010 --> 00:53:25,960
about what
the life of rich people is like?

1157
00:53:26,460 --> 00:53:27,980
Let's imagine

1158
00:53:27,980 --> 00:53:30,760
that rich people must be
living in luxury

1159
00:53:30,760 --> 00:53:31,900
and able to get anything they want,

1160
00:53:31,900 --> 00:53:33,520
drive luxury cars and live in mansions.

1161
00:53:35,340 --> 00:53:37,270
I do have luxury cars and mansions.

1162
00:53:37,690 --> 00:53:39,590
But I don't have the right to use them.

1163
00:53:39,780 --> 00:53:40,620
What do I mean?

1164
00:53:40,860 --> 00:53:42,510
My car is driven by my driver.

1165
00:53:42,510 --> 00:53:43,420
He drives it every day.

1166
00:53:43,420 --> 00:53:44,860
I don't even have a driver's license.

1167
00:53:44,860 --> 00:53:45,720
My nanny

1168
00:53:45,730 --> 00:53:46,760
