more than a few times a year.

1171
00:53:49,740 --> 00:53:50,580
So,

1172
00:53:50,940 --> 00:53:52,960
what is the life of rich people
really like?

1173
00:53:53,260 --> 00:53:55,060
I will ask them both tonight
when I get back.

1174
00:53:55,300 --> 00:53:56,590
Zhang and Li,

1175
00:53:56,700 --> 00:53:57,740
what is your life as rich people

1176
00:53:57,740 --> 00:53:59,270
really like?

1177
00:54:05,780 --> 00:54:06,620
Moreover,

1178
00:54:09,820 --> 00:54:12,610
