1182
00:54:17,460 --> 00:54:19,940
filled with insincere smiles
and hollow pleasantries,

1183
00:54:19,940 --> 00:54:21,420
which is simply nauseating.

1184
00:54:21,420 --> 00:54:24,490
Moreover, we are constantly travelling
for meetings around the world,

1185
00:54:24,490 --> 00:54:25,860
with busy schedules and jobs,

1186
00:54:25,860 --> 00:54:28,210
