the details of life,

1187
00:54:28,210 --> 00:54:29,080
such as

1188
00:54:29,080 --> 00:54:30,490
a warm dinner with family

1189
00:54:30,490 --> 00:54:33,130
or the time spent with children.

1190
00:54:33,130 --> 00:54:35,080
Well, I don't have children yet.

1191
00:54:35,860 --> 00:54:38,900
So these things that are easily
accessible to ordinary people

1192
00:54:38,900 --> 00:54:40,740
are actually the real wealth.

1193
00:54:40,740 --> 00:54:42,340
So from certain perspectives,

1194
00:54:42,340 --> 00:54:44,110
you are relatively rich,

1195
00:54:44,380 --> 00:54:46,400
while I am absolutely rich.

1196
00:55:01,340 --> 00:55:02,840
So, my friends,

1197
00:55:03,210 --> 00:55:04,150
the life of rich people

1198
